title: Women and Children Are Main Victims of the Israel-Hamas War With 16,000 Killed, U.N. Says
description: Women and children are the main victims in the Israel-Hamas war, with some 16,000 killed, the United Nations agency said.

title: Sports Illustrated at the Bottom of the Ninth
description: For the first time since 1954, fans of sports or journalism, or both, must ask: Who are we without SI? writes John Walters.

title: Delivery Firm’s AI Chatbot Goes Rogue, Curses at Customer and Criticizes Company
description: An AI customer service chatbot for delivery service DPD used profanity and criticized the company after prompting by a frustrated customer.

title: U.K. Police Warn of ‘Unprecedented’ Rise in Terrorism Threat Amid Israel-Hamas War
description: The U.K.’s most senior counter-terrorism officer warns there's been an “unprecedented” spike in terrorism threats amid the Israel-Hamas war.

title: Wisconsin Republicans Introduce Bill to Ban Abortions After 14 Weeks of Pregnancy
description: Republicans introduced a bill that would call for a statewide referendum on whether abortion should be banned after 14 weeks of pregnancy.

title: Ava DuVernay on the Urgency and Artistry of Historical Drama Origin
description: Ava DuVernay's new film, 'Origin,' is based on Isabel Wilkerson's 2020 book 'Caste: The Origins of Our Discontents.'

title: The Message the Ram Temple Sends Muslims Like Me
description: An eerie feeling looms over many Indian Muslims ahead of the Lord Ram Temple inauguration on Jan. 22.
